lyrics:
[Verse]
In the heart of the night, we gather tonight
Glynn's birthday party, shining so bright
With electric guitars, we'll set the stage on fire
Embracing our freedom, we'll reach even higher

[Chorus]
Oh, it's Glynn's birthday tonight
Let the rock 'n' roll take flight
We'll sing our hearts out, scream and shout
In this sweet celebration, there's no doubt
